OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776269466
OL,3,CMan who left businesswoman partner
OL,4,Cbrain damaged jailed
OL,6,FA businesswoman was forced to quit
OL,7,Fwork and "leave the community she
OL,8,Floved" after an attack by her partner
OL,9,Fleft her brain damaged.
OL,11,FPeter Sowerby, 63, assaulted the woman
OL,12,Fat the Cocketts Hotel in Hawes, North
OL,13,FYorkshire, where they lived, after
OL,14,Fthey had a night out with friends in
OL,15,FAugust 2021.
OL,17,FHe pushed her to the floor, sat on top
OL,18,Fof her and repeatedly punched and
OL,19,Fkicked her. She only managed to escape
OL,20,Fafter biting his finger, North
OL,21,FYorkshire Police said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
