PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776269466
OL,3,CMan who left businesswoman partner
OL,4,Cbrain damaged jailed
OL,6,FThe woman, who ran two hotels and a
OL,7,Fnewsagents, was taken to hospital with
OL,8,Fbruising, swelling and bleeding on the
OL,9,Fbrain.
OL,11,FPolice said she continues to suffer
OL,12,Fseizures more than four years on.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "She can no
OL,15,Flonger work, has had to move away from
OL,16,Fa community she loved, and has lost
OL,17,Fmoney from her successful businesses,
OL,18,Fall because of Sowerby's horrific
OL,19,Fattack."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
