PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776269466
OL,3,CMan who left businesswoman partner
OL,4,Cbrain damaged jailed
OL,6,FSowerby, who now lives in Tiverton,
OL,7,FDevon, left the UK after the attack
OL,8,Fand set up a business in Thailand,
OL,9,Fleaving the victim to deal with the
OL,10,Fsale of the businesses in the UK and
OL,11,Fsettle his debts.
OL,13,FHe was found guilty of causing
OL,14,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent after
OL,15,Fa trial and was jailed for five-and-a-
OL,16,Fhalf years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
