OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776269466
OL,3,CMan who left businesswoman partner
OL,4,Cbrain damaged jailed
OL,6,FDet Con Martin Willoughby said: "The
OL,7,Fvictim and her family have shown
OL,8,Funwavering support for the
OL,9,Finvestigation, resulting in a man who
OL,10,Fis a danger to women being put behind
OL,11,Fbars.
OL,13,F"The victim truly deserves some
OL,14,Fhappiness and I hope that this court
OL,15,Fresult helps bring some closure for
OL,16,Fher following a horrendous ordeal."
